reviewText: About Josh Kirby Time Warrior-Trapped in Toy-world was well performance of acting in imagination world when Josh Kirby was trapped in fanastyland of Toy-world and has some fun in it for all people to enjoy only this video. This was good acting and would recommend this VHS for Hearing Impaired since the VHS is closed-captioned that is only in VHS and it is not in any DVDs for Josh Kirby Time Warrior collections. This is recommended for all ages of all general audiences to watch the collections of VHS in Josh Kirby Time Warrior!
